data.description: OVER 42 acres with immaculate Quad  Manor Manufactured home on permanent foundation;  with amazing views of lake/river, mountains and trees.  Pasture and gated with one other neighbor.  Gorgeous pastures surround; parcel went to lakes edge; however, with dam removal eminent next year the water line will be the Klamath River with unknown water levels.  Deluxe interior, vaulted and 9' ceilings; open kitchen with endless cabinetry and lovely island which includes a jenn aire downdraft range, double ovens and large pantry.  Rooms are large, living room has slider to deck as well as dining area.  Open kitchen/dining and great room that boasts a real fireplace!  Decking on 3 sides to enjoy all the views.  Detached 36x25 garage/shop with additional concreted area for more vehicles or toys!  Some furnishings included. This is a spectacular end of the road that is gated along with neighboring residence.  Lots of possibilities!
